name: BetaPro Gold Bullion 2x Daily Bull ETF
longDescription: GLDU seeks daily investment results, before fees, expenses, distributions, brokerage commissions and other times (200 percent) the daily performance of the Solactive Gold Front Month MD Rolling Futures Index ER. HBU is denominated in Canadian dollars. GLDU does not seek to achieve its stated investment objective over a period of time greater than one day.
